data.description: Fantastic move in ready 3 bedroom 2 bath all one level home with brand new arch shingle roof 2023! Welcoming foyer with higher than standard ceilings that lead you to the living room with ceiling fan! Kitchen with nice tiled backsplash, new faucet, range, built in microwave, dishwasher & refrigerator stays! Dining room! Owners suite with tray ceiling, fan, walk in closet, bathroom with long vanity! Spacious spare bedroom! Bathroom with new faucet! New carpet! Laundry room! Covered porch with extended patio, raised garden beds & great firepit area overlooking privacy fenced backyard & storage building stays! Two car garage! Great location with easy access to shopping, parks, restaurants & more!
